{"tid":1321268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不斷有人盜用我資料，係facebook進行撐警活動。","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:19:19.000Z","uid":103131,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7126f10f89aa380f98052d0d8e215a7cb60aa6","tid":1321268,"uid":103131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:26:47.000Z","msg":"如題，有個人不斷係facebook用我既照片開假AC，去召集人撐警同埋開撐警群組。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好困擾同好憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n已經舉報過幾次，佢每次都開新AC。<br />\n想請問有咩方法可以杜絕呢種情況，真係好苦惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5022ca435101b68b02ef3c29d1e17daa2c1820b9","tid":1321268,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"絲打你好出名？"},{"pid":"e2867791d73a6437bffae03057448b902206cdf6","tid":1321268,"uid":41888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"928d8a710a1f95e6bf0498cdc3b85bd392d8d849","tid":1321268,"uid":103131,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5022ca435101b68b02ef3c29d1e17daa2c1820b9","tid":1321268,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"絲打你好出名？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:30:45.000Z","msg":"唔出名，小薯仔一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開佢Facebook，裏面全部都係我D相。仲係度用我名義慫恿D人撐警，係度自稱「小妹」，我覺得好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f2f769e26555af866169f796fb27be729ec3d0","tid":1321268,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:32:14.000Z","msg":"一定好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4dd5859d313849054d150fc77b6b619bcae7e6","tid":1321268,"uid":103131,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"佢之前仲用個假AC宣揚派錢撐警，叫人聯絡佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\